****[Bitcoin Exchange](ANX) is a trading platform for buying and selling bitcoin in AUD, CAD, CHF, EUR, GBP, HKD, JPY, NZD, SGD and USD currencies . The exchange was established in 2013 and is legally registered and based in Hong Kong.  Asia Nexgen was one of the first Bitcoin exchanges in Hong Kong to be issued with a Money Services Operator (MSO) license by the Hong Kong Customs and Excise Department.  The trading engine is built upon the LMAX Disruptor technology used by banks for their foreign currency exchange (FX) trading.  The engine was designed to handle high volume, high throughput, and low latency trading.  The exchange has a favorable reputation for promptly processing deposit and withdrawal requests on a weekday daily basis.

